11 An Act relating to cities and towns; amending 11 O.S.
2021, Section 51-104b, which relates to the
12 prevention of unfair labor practice; modifying Public
Employees Relations Board powers; establishing
13 process for arbitrator selection in cases of unfair
labor practices; amending 11 O.S. 2021, Section 51-
14 110, which relates to fees and expenses; modifying
applicability; providing for codification; and
15 providing an effective date.
